▪ Remove the container
▪ Remove the image

 [rshdan@localhost ~]$ docker container stop 0d14c5626101
 0d14c5626101
 [rshdan@localhost ~]$ docker container rm 0d14c5626101
 0d14c5626101
 [rshdan@localhost ~]$ docker image ls
 REPOSITORY    TAG       IMAGE ID       CREATED        SIZE
 hello-world   latest    74cc54e27dc4   2 months ago   10.1kB
 [rshdan@localhost ~]$ docker rmi 74cc54e27dc4
